### Health Check (Root)
GET http://localhost:8000/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Health Check (Detailed)
GET http://localhost:8000/health HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### List Models
# Returns "meta-model" plus all available underlying provider models
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/models HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Get Usage Statistics
# Shows global token and request counts
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/usage HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Chat Completion (Meta-Model)
# Automatically selects the best available provider/model
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "meta-model",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "What are Medford OR known for?"}
    ],
    "temperature": 0.7
}

### Chat Completion ( Romania Inquiry )
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "meta-model",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "Format response in JSON."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "When was the country Romania founded?"}
    ]
}

### Specific Model Routing
# Directly target a specific provider and model
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "Mistral/mistral-large-latest",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of France?"}
    ]
}

### JSON Output Format Hint
# Injects system instructions to ensure JSON output
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "meta-model",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "List 3 colors in a JSON array."}
  ],
  "response_format": {
    "type": "json_object"
  }
}

### Filter Models by Type (coding)
# Returns only coding models across all providers
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/models?type=coding HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Filter Models by Scale (large)
# Returns only large-scale models (70B+ parameters)
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/models?scale=large HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Filter Models by Type and Scale
# Returns coding models with medium scale
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/models?type=coding&scale=medium HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Chat Completion with Coding Model
# Use a coding-optimized model for code generation
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "Mistral/codestral-latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a Python function to merge two sorted lists."}
  ]
}

### Chat Completion with Large Model
# Use a large-scale model for complex reasoning
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "Cerebras/qwen-3-235b-a22b-instruct-2507",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Explain the philosophical implications of artificial general intelligence."}
  ]
}

### Chat Completion with Medium Model
# Use a medium-scale model for balanced performance
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "Groq/qwen/qwen3-32b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Summarize the key features of Python 3.12 in 3 bullet points."}
  ]
}

### Chat Completion with Type Filter (coding)
# Auto-select a coding model without specifying exact model name
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "meta-model",
  "model_type": "coding",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a Python function to check if a string is a palindrome."}
  ]
}

### Chat Completion with Scale Filter (large)
# Auto-select a large-scale model for complex tasks
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "meta-model",
  "model_scale": "large",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Analyze the economic implications of artificial intelligence on job markets."}
  ]
}

### Chat Completion with Type and Scale Filter
# Auto-select a medium-scale coding model
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "meta-model",
  "model_type": "coding",
  "model_scale": "medium",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Refactor this code to use list comprehension: squares = []; for i in range(10): squares.append(i**2)"}
  ]
}
